"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-raygun-retiring-breakdancing-paris-olympics-b2644814.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The breaker was mocked online for her performance at 2024 Olympics Games  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Australian breakdancer Rachael Gunn clarified that she's not retiring from thesportaftershe said last week that she would notbe participating in any more competitions.\", \"from\": 396, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 420, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9995726167051837, \"rank\": 0.0002943885214075684, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 443, \"end\": 450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.4178073960078827e-12, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 451, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.8044713997892726, \"rank\": 0.23947615334624692, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn, also known as \\\"B-girl Raygun\\\",went viral on the internetalmost overnight in August after sheperformed unusual movesat the 2024 ParisOlympics, includinga kangaroo hop and a wriggle on the floor.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 589, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.8044713997892726, \"rank\": 0.23947615334624692, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interview last week, she said the scrutiny and backlash over her performance at the Olympics resulted in her wanting to retire.\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just did not have any control over how people saw me or who I was.\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was going to keep competing, for sure, but that seems really difficult for me to do now,\\\" she told local radio station2DayFM.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the level of scrutiny that's going to be there, and people will be filming it, and it will go online.\\\"\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I still break but that's like, in my living room with my partner,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, in a new interview, she has now said she is not retiring and that her comments were taken out of context.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not a decision that I did come to, this turned into a story.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I wastalking, you know, on2dayFMabout how I am not going to do certain competitions anymore, which did not seem like such a big deal becausebreakingis not going to be in the Olympics any way,\\\" she saidon theTodayshowon Monday.\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But you know, I am still going to be part of community jams, or I'd like to go to community jams and still dance and still break.\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I never used the word retire - I am not retiring.\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You try and stop me, I am not ever going to stop dancing so if you hear that again, you know that it's not the truth,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She said breaking was a \\\"lifestyle\\\" and \\\"you can not retire from culture\\\".\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You can not retire from an art form.\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So that's why I am never going to stop.\\\"\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old university lecturer from Sydney lost all three of her round-robin contests at the Olympics by a combined score of 54-0 and was ridiculed for her moves on social media.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2239, \"end\": 2245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999960037896739, \"rank\": 3.5487264723135783e-06, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn's performance led to a petition that called for an apology from the athlete as well as Australia's Olympic chef de mission Anna Meares.\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2383, \"end\": 2387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.8044713997892726, \"rank\": 0.23947615334624692, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 2475, \"end\": 2484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9924261229700834, \"rank\": 0.005733689543797399, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2511, \"end\": 2522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anna Meares\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Meares\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The petition received over 50,000 signatures and derided Gunn and Meares for \\\"attempting to gaslight the public and undermining the efforts of genuine athletes\\\".\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She described the response to herperformance \\\"devastating\\\".\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2746, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd really like to ask the press to please stop harassing my family, my friends, the Australian breaking community and the broader street dance community,\\\" she said in an Instagram video at the time.\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2834, \"end\": 2844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9995726167051837, \"rank\": 0.0002943885214075684, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 2920, \"end\": 2929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.667308057074441e-25, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone has been through a lot as a result of this, so I ask you to please respect their privacy.\\\"\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 3050, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3103, \"end\": 3114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 6.097505430956997e-13, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"